<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title><![CDATA[Blog by Joshua Jones]]></title><description><![CDATA[Personal site of Joshua Jones a Mechanical Engineer building Software Engineering skills in 2020.]]></description><link>https://jonesprojects.co.uk</link><generator>GatsbyJS</generator><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 23:56:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><item><title><![CDATA[Hello 2020!]]></title><description><![CDATA[how I got here]]></description><link>https://jonesprojects.co.uk/posts/2020 is the year of embracing code</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jonesprojects.co.uk/posts/2020 is the year of embracing code</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h1 id=&quot;2020-is-the-year-of-embracing-code&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#2020-is-the-year-of-embracing-code&quot; aria-label=&quot;2020 is the year of embracing code permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2020 is the year of embracing code.&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My first work experience in high school was learning some Java interning over the summer at a small software company. I learned a lot but decided code wasn’t for me.
I felt much more at home making physical stuff so I went to study mechanical engineering instead. I learned, built, and got a masters degree along the way. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Code did keep pulling me back every now and then, while interning for cummins turbo technologies I wrote data analysis scripts in Python as one of the few people in my department who could.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After my masters degree I went into programme (project) management at Aston Martin launching new models. I spent 2 years at Aston Martin and during that time I started taking tutorials on &lt;a href=&quot;http://freecodecamp.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;freecodecamp.com&lt;/a&gt; to learn fullstack javascript development just as a hobby.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I found a &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.ycombinator.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;https://news.ycombinator.com/&lt;/a&gt; “who’s hiring?” thread for a programming job, completed a few take home tests and some team-fit calls and now I work for an American start up company that is fully remote! Since September I’ve been writing Javascript everyday at home!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;what-im-learning-in-january&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#what-im-learning-in-january&quot; aria-label=&quot;what im learning in january permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;What I’m learning in January&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ReactJS  - which incidentally is how this blog is made.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Redux&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Typescript  &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[How I built this site with GatsbyJS]]></title><description><![CDATA[A Super simple guide to building a blog with gatsby and using github-pages to host]]></description><link>https://jonesprojects.co.uk/posts/How to build this site</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://jonesprojects.co.uk/posts/How to build this site</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;h2 id=&quot;a-super-simple-guide-to-building-a-blog-with-gatsby-and-using-github-pages-to-host&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#a-super-simple-guide-to-building-a-blog-with-gatsby-and-using-github-pages-to-host&quot; aria-label=&quot;a super simple guide to building a blog with gatsby and using github pages to host permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;A Super simple guide to building a blog with gatsby and using github-pages to host:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;what-is-gatsbyjs&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#what-is-gatsbyjs&quot; aria-label=&quot;what is gatsbyjs permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;What is GatsbyJS?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A static site generator for ReactJS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;what-is-lumen&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#what-is-lumen&quot; aria-label=&quot;what is lumen permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;What is Lumen?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A minimal, lightweight and mobile-first starter for creating blogs using Gatsby. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;getting-set-up&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#getting-set-up&quot; aria-label=&quot;getting set up permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Getting set up&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Install node &lt;a href=&quot;https://nodejs.org/en/download/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;https://nodejs.org/en/download/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Install gatsby&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;npm install -g gatsby-cli&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;create-a-gatsby-site&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#create-a-gatsby-site&quot; aria-label=&quot;create a gatsby site permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Create a Gatsby site&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use the Gatsby CLI to create a new site, specifying the Lumen starter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;gatsby new blog https://github.com/alxshelepenok/gatsby-starter-lumen&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;start-developing&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#start-developing&quot; aria-label=&quot;start developing permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Start Developing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Navigate into your new site’s directory and start it up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;gatsby-highlight&quot; data-language=&quot;sh&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-sh&quot;&gt;cd blog
gatsby develop&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;open-the-source-code-and-start-editing&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#open-the-source-code-and-start-editing&quot; aria-label=&quot;open the source code and start editing permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Open the source code and start editing!&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your site is now running at &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8000&lt;/code&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;how-to-actually-edit-stuff-the-simple-way&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#how-to-actually-edit-stuff-the-simple-way&quot; aria-label=&quot;how to actually edit stuff the simple way permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;How to actually edit stuff the simple way&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are a bunch of files and folders in the /blog/ folder that are needed to build the site, to actually edit the blog to your own content there are a small number of folders and files you actually have to edit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;important-files-and-folders&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#important-files-and-folders&quot; aria-label=&quot;important files and folders permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Important files and folders&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/content/pages holds the about and contact pages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/Content/posts holds the blog posts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/config.js holds the meta data for the site and social media accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/static/photo.jpg holds the picture for the user pic and the favicon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;/static/media holds pictures and other media assets for blog posts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;developing&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#developing&quot; aria-label=&quot;developing permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Developing&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can make edits to blog posts &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;(.md)&lt;/code&gt; files and save and the localhost:8000 page in your browser will auto-load your changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To see edits to config.js you need to stop the &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;gatsby develop&lt;/code&gt; command (usually ctrl+c in your terminal) and run it again.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;publishing-to-github-pages&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#publishing-to-github-pages&quot; aria-label=&quot;publishing to github pages permalink&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot;&gt;&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; focusable=&quot;false&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; version=&quot;1.1&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 16 16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt;&lt;path fill-rule=&quot;evenodd&quot; d=&quot;M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Publishing to github pages&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;npm run deploy &amp;#x3C; - this builds the site to the &lt;code class=&quot;language-text&quot;&gt;/public&lt;/code&gt; folder this is the folder to upload to github pages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;move the contents of public to your gh-pages repository and the site will build from there in a few minutes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content:encoded></item></channel></rss>